Code preview of the table CON_优惠明细表

drop table "CON_DiscountItem" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_DiscountItem" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_DiscountItem"
(
"DiscountItemID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"MainDiscountID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"DiscounttCode" VARCHAR2(30) not null,
"DiscountItemTypeCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"DiscountItemTypeName" NVARCHAR2(100) not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"DisDurationDays" INTEGER not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"DisItemPrice" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"DisItemAmount" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"Percent" NUMBER(10,2),
"ReductionType" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"DisReasonID" INTEGER not null,
"DisReasonCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"OtherReasons" NVARCHAR2(1000),
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_CON_DISCOUNTITEM primary key ("DiscountItemID")
);

comment on column "CON_DiscountItem"."DiscountItemTypeCode" is
'10:租金单价
20:装修期
30: 免租
40: 其他';

comment on column "CON_DiscountItem"."ReductionType" is
'1:周期性
2:一次性';

comment on column "CON_DiscountItem"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0：无效';
